src:
Winning numbers drawn in 'Numbers Midday' game
02 Nov 2019, 17:40 by The Associated Press
CRANSTON, R.I. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Saturday afternoon's drawing of the Rhode Island Lottery's "Numbers Midday" game were:
2-5-2-5
(two, five, two, five)
